Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用盡全力掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:18.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將親眼見到的未來
